abstract: A look around the nation at the best in college football from Week 8.
snippet: A look around the nation at the best in college football from Week 8.
lead_paragraph: ZACH COLLAROS The senior Cincinnati quarterback threw for three touchdowns and ran for two more in the fourth quarter, helping Cincinnati come from behind in the closing minutes to stay atop the Big East standings with a 37-34 victory against host South Florida. Collaros finished 26 of 41 passing for 389 yards.

headline.main: The Day's Best in College Football
